Author: Giorgio Speranza [aut,cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1478-0995>) 
Maintainer: Giorgio Speranza <speranza@fbk.eu>
Description: Package dedicated to the analysis of X ray Photoelectron Spectra.
             It provides a number of options making the spectral analysis easy.
             RxpsG also contains powerful graphical options for data representation. 
Depends: R (>= 3.0.2), digest, gWidgets2, gWidgets2tcltk, import, 
          latticeExtra  
Imports: graphics, grDevices, methods, minpack.lm, signal, stats, utils
